OL,3,CGovernment must go further, report
OL,4,Cinto calls for 'Hillsborough Law' finds
OL,6,FThe Government must go further to
OL,7,Favoid a repeat of the failures made
OL,8,Fafter major tragedies like the
OL,9,FHillsborough disaster, MPs and peers
OL,10,Fhave warned
OL,12,FA report into calls for a
OL,13,F"Hillsborough Law", published by
OL,14,FParliament's Joint Committee on Human
OL,15,FRights (JCHR) on Friday, found
OL,16,F"institutional defensiveness" remained
OL,17,Fa problem and recommended the
OL,18,FGovernment consider introducing a
OL,19,Fstatutory duty of candour for all
OL,20,Fpublic bodies.
