OL,3,CGovernment must go further, report
OL,4,Cinto calls for 'Hillsborough Law' finds
OL,6,FCampaigners want new legislation to
OL,7,Fprevent the experiences of families of
OL,8,Fthe 97 Liverpool fans who were killed
OL,9,Fin the 1989 Hillsborough disaster
OL,10,Fhappening again.
OL,12,FIt would include a legal duty of
OL,13,Fcandour, guaranteed legal funding for
OL,14,Fbereaved families at inquests and
OL,15,Finquiries and an independent public
OL,16,Fadvocate.
