OL,6,FCalls for the law to be introduced
OL,7,Fwere repeated earlier this week
OL,8,Ffollowing the report of the Infected
OL,9,FBlood Inquiry, which found the scandal
OL,10,F"could largely have been avoided" and
OL,11,Fthere was a "pervasive" cover-up to
OL,12,Fhide the truth.
