OL,3,CGovernment must go further, report
OL,4,Cinto calls for 'Hillsborough Law' finds
OL,6,FJCHR chairwoman Joanna Cherry KC said:
OL,7,F"All of us on the human rights
OL,8,Fcommittee have huge respect and
OL,9,Fadmiration for the courage and
OL,10,Ffortitude of the families of those who
OL,11,Fdied at Hillsborough and the
OL,12,Fsurvivors. Just this week we have also
OL,13,Fseen how the victims of the infected
OL,14,Fblood scandal had to go through a
OL,15,Fsimilar struggle.
OL,17,F"It is shameful that their pain was
OL,18,Fcompounded by the delays and
OL,19,Fobfuscation they faced in their search
OL,20,Ffor the truth, and the decades they
OL,21,Fhad to wait for justice.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
