OL,3,CGovernment must go further, report
OL,4,Cinto calls for 'Hillsborough Law' finds
OL,6,F"Even so many years later, lessons
OL,7,Fstill have to be learnt to ensure that
OL,8,Fthese failures are not repeated.
OL,10,F"We are calling on the Government to
OL,11,Fmake sure there are cast-iron measures
OL,12,Fin place that give families as much
OL,13,Fclout at investigations as the public
OL,14,Fbodies whose reputations are at risk.
OL,16,F"We also want to see more widespread
OL,17,Fmeasures to establish a culture of
OL,18,Fopenness to ensure the truth is not
OL,19,Fhidden from the public and those
OL,20,Finvolved."
