OL,3,CGovernment must go further, report
OL,4,Cinto calls for 'Hillsborough Law' finds
OL,6,FLast year, in a response to a report
OL,7,Ffrom former bishop of Liverpool the
OL,8,FRight Rev James Jones, the Government
OL,9,Fstopped short of introducing
OL,10,Flegislation.
OL,12,FInstead, it signed up to a
OL,13,FHillsborough Charter, pledging to
OL,14,Fplace the public interest above its
OL,15,Fown reputation.
OL,17,FIt has also announced plans for an
OL,18,Findependent public advocate (IPA) to
OL,19,Fsupport those affected by major
OL,20,Fdisasters.
