OL,3,CGovernment must go further, report
OL,4,Cinto calls for 'Hillsborough Law' finds
OL,6,FIn its report, the JCHR said
OL,7,Fdevelopments indicated the Government
OL,8,Fwas "at last listening".
OL,10,FIt added: "We welcome these steps but
OL,11,Fare not persuaded that they go far
OL,12,Fenough ` particularly in relation to
OL,13,Fthe creation of a broad statutory duty
OL,14,Fof candour for all public authorities
OL,15,Fand their employees.
OL,17,F"It has taken too long to reach this
OL,18,Fpoint. We urge the Government not to
OL,19,Flose this new impetus."
