OL,3,CGovernment must go further, report
OL,4,Cinto calls for 'Hillsborough Law' finds
OL,6,FThe committee said it heard from
OL,7,Fwitnesses who felt the lessons of
OL,8,FHillsborough "remained unlearnt" and
OL,9,Fsome of the same issues continued to
OL,10,Fhave an impact at other major hearings
OL,11,F` such as the Manchester Arena inquiry
OL,12,F` and in inquests taking place daily.
OL,14,FThe report said there remained a "real
OL,15,Frisk of inequality of arms" between
OL,16,Fpublic bodies appearing before
OL,17,Finquests or inquiries and bereaved
OL,18,Ffamilies which may "damage the ability
OL,19,Fof inquests to get to the truth of
OL,20,Fevents".
