OL,3,CGovernment must go further, report
OL,4,Cinto calls for 'Hillsborough Law' finds
OL,6,FIt said: "We urge the Government to
OL,7,Ftake steps to ensure that families
OL,8,Freceive proportionate legal
OL,9,Frepresentation at inquests and
OL,10,Finquiries whenever the state has its
OL,11,Fown representation."
OL,13,FThe committee welcomed the creation of
OL,14,Fadvocates for victims of major
OL,15,Fincidents but said it was crucial
OL,16,Fappointments were not delayed.
OL,18,FSolicitor Elkan Abrahamson, a director
OL,19,Fof the Hillsborough Law Now campaign,
OL,20,Fsaid: "It feels like we're at a
OL,21,Ftipping point.
