OL,3,CGovernment must go further, report
OL,4,Cinto calls for 'Hillsborough Law' finds
OL,6,F"Just this week we have seen Sir Brian
OL,7,FLangtsaff at the Infected Bloody
OL,8,FInquiry demand a statutory duty of
OL,9,Fcandour and as each week has gone by
OL,10,Fat the Post Office Inquiry the
OL,11,Fwidespread cover-up is being exposed.
OL,13,F"We have to reverse this culture where
OL,14,Fpublic officials lie at will. How hard
OL,15,Fis it to tell the truth?
OL,17,F"It has to stop now before more lives
OL,18,Fare ruined. The next government must
OL,19,Fput the enactment of a duty of candour
OL,20,Flaw at the top of their to do list."
